       SUEZ and the European Union Federations sign a European agreement
       to strengthen professional equality
       SUEZ will adapt all of its businesses to make them accessible to
       both women and men. The agreement also provides for actions to
       deconstruct stereotypes and zero tolerance for sexual harassment.
