The Fondation SUEZ

   Myriam Bincaille-Delegate General of the Fonds SUEZ initiatives

     Promote social inclusion is our mission. By supporting our partners,
     we increase access to essential services for disadvantaged
     populations in developing countries and we fight against social
     exclusion in France.

     Myriam Bincaille-Delegate General of the Fondation SUEZ

   (BUTTON) Our Areas of Action
